Feature: Accounts
	As a restaurant owner
	I want to login/out
	So that I can update details on my website

	Scenario: Login
		Given I have an account
		And I hit the login link on the home page
		Then I should be able to sign in using my email and password

	Scenario: Logout
		Given I am logged in
		And I hit the logout link
		Then I should be logged out